{
  "texts": [
    "In comparison, 12% and 13% of the participants from G N A R and G N A N R said they added a title; a participant from G N A R wrote: \"I [originally] did not give my recipe a title.",
    "I saw that in the example recipe and realised stating the title would help the presentation\".",
    "Additionally, to comprehend the impact of the reflective prompts, we examined how participants in groups G A R and G N A R responded regarding their utilization of these prompts.",
    "Among the participants, 27% mentioned that the prompts were useful in identifying areas of improvement, with one participant expressing, \"I had to actually think about where I was going wrong and what was good about the example\".",
    "For 12% of the participants, the reflective prompts acted as a means of introspection, leading them to consider ways to enhance their own recipe writing."
  ]
}